org.transitime.maintenance

Class AwsGlacierInventoryRetriever

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.maintenance.AwsGlacierInventoryRetriever

  • public class AwsGlacierInventoryRetriever
extends java.lang.Object
    For retrieving an AWS Glacier inventory file for a vault. The inventory file shows all of the entries in the inventory along with the archiveId. This archiveId can be used to upload the data stored in glacier.
    Author:
    SkiBu Smith
